node.title: Serious crash between car and motorbike on Auckland's southern motorway
node.description: Two lanes have been closed after the accident in Ellerslie.
node.content: ["Two lanes have been closed on Auckland's southern motorway after a serious crash in Ellerslie.", "Police say the accident between a car and a motorbike happened about 1:45pm in the northbound lanes.\u00a0", "\"One person has sustained serious injuries,\" a police spokesperson says.", "\"Two northbound lanes will be closed while emergency services are at the scene.\"", "The serious crash unit has been advised."]
